---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
const links = [
  { label: 'Claude',          href: '/categoria/claude' },
  { label: 'Novas IAs',       href: '/categoria/novas-ias' },
  { label: 'Atualizações',    href: '/categoria/atualizacoes' },
  { label: 'MCPs',            href: '/categoria/mcps' },
  { label: 'Skills & Agents', href: '/categoria/agents' },
];
---

<footer class="mt-20 border-t border-[rgba(255,255,255,0.08)] bg-[#0a0a0a]">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 py-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-10 sm:grid-cols-3">
      <!-- Marca -->
      <div class="col-span-1">
        <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <img src="/logo.svg" alt="AIgora" class="h-7 w-auto" />
        </a>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-[#b3b3b3] leading-relaxed max-w-xs">
          O melhor da inteligência artificial — Claude, MCPs, Agents, novas IAs e muito mais.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Categorias -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#b3b3b3] mb-4">Categorias</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          {links.map(({ label, href }) => (
            <li>
              <a href={href} class="text-sm text-[#b3b3b3] hover:text-white transition-colors">{label}</a>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Newsletter -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#b3b3b3] mb-4">Newsletter</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-[#b3b3b3] mb-4">
          Receba o compilado das principais notícias a cada quinzena.
        </p>
        <a href="/newsletter" class="inline-flex rounded-full border border-[#00BCD4] px-5 py-2.5 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#00BCD4] hover:bg-[#00BCD4] hover:text-white transition-all duration-300">
          Inscrever-se grátis
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 border-t border-[rgba(255,255,255,0.06)] pt-6 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3">
      <p class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-[#b3b3b3]/40">© {year} AIgora. Todos os direitos reservados.</p>
      <p class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-[#b3b3b3]/40">Feito com <span class="text-[#00BCD4]">♥</span> no Brasil</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
